fields.title: Avengers: Endgame
fields.tagline: Part of the journey is the end
fields.description: After the devastating events of Avengers: Infinity War, the universe is in ruins. The remaining Avengers must assemble once again to undo Thanos' actions and restore order to the universe.

fields.title: Joker
fields.description: In Gotham City, mentally-troubled comedian Arthur Fleck embarks on a downward spiral of revolution and bloody crime. This path brings him face-to-face with his alter-ego
